metadata.name: Alpha Mutant Genesis
metadata.description: Known as Alpha Mutants, they possess powerful mutant Alpha-Genes, which grant them super-human abilities. Holders of one will also be able to access the Alpha Mutants discord, where they will have access to the Alpha section and tools, including wallet trackers, project analyses, alpha calls, degen plays, airdrops, market analysis, raffles, and giveaways. Additional features will include node access, partnered tools, and Treasury yield payouts.
